# ── Duplicate / copy junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# macOS Finder / editor / chat-export flows create "<name> 2.<ext>" copies and
# merge-recovery leaves "<name>.collision-backup.md". These caused real damage:
# untracked copies blocked rebases/merges and diverged the working tree. Ignore
# them so they can never be tracked, committed, or clutter `git status`.
# (Delete the originals-of-value, not these — these are always throwaway copies.)
* [0-9].md
* [0-9].ts
* [0-9].tsx
* [0-9].js
* [0-9].jsx
* [0-9].json
* [0-9].yml
* [0-9].yaml
* [0-9].sh
* [0-9].tsbuildinfo
*.collision-backup.md

# TypeScript incremental build info (backend + any stray copies)
*.tsbuildinfo
# Orphaned / stuck Next.js build output (root or web)
.next
.next.stuck-*
web/.next.stuck-*
